2.caption: 1979 NFL Pro Bowl
2.description: The 1979 Pro Bowl was the NFL's 29th annual all-star game which featured the outstanding performers from the 1978 season. The game was played on Monday, January 29, 1979, at Los Angeles Memorial Coliseum in Los Angeles, California before a crowd of 38,333. The final score was NFC 13, AFC 7.
2.inspected:Announcers: Frank Gifford, Howard Cosell and Don Meredith
2.inspected:Stadium: Los Angeles Memorial Coliseum, Los Angeles, California
